 SN feedback, that feedback mechanisms other than SNe are\nimportant, or that other aspects of galaxy evolution, such as star formation,\nrequire better treatment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Sep 2016 20:00:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Nov 2016 12:08:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-25"}
