 seems to be correlated, in all cases,\nwith the morphological structure of the CME as derived from visible-light\nimages.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2016 08:02:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-19"}
