ow which the IO cannot sink. We show that the value\nof $g_c$ depends on the characteristics of both the IO and the granular bed,as\nwell as on the initial IO's depth.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2016 09:30:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 17 Dec 2016 06:17:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-04"}
